  "history": "The client has a history of recurring conflicts and strained relationships, often marked by trust and boundary issues. Some relationships have involved alcoholism, which may have contributed to emotional distress and instability. There is a pattern of aggressive behavior, possibly as a defensive response to perceived threats or betrayals. These interpersonal difficulties have likely reinforced feelings of isolation and difficulty forming secure attachments.",
